title: Teen Pop - Volume 1
description: 10 happy and catchy melodies for your social games, visual novels, dating and sim games
longDescription:
Preview the collection:

  • YouTube


"Teen Pop - Volume 1" features 10 catchy and upbeat melodies with electronic and acoustic elements. Suitable for your teen visual novels, anime and sim, adventures, RPG, dating and any social mobile game. Take advantage of "short" edits, "no fade in" versions and multiple loops taken from every section.


  • Rush Hour: Full length (01:32), 6 Short edits, 15 Loops
  • Tropical Party: Full length (02:01), 3 Short edits, 15 Loops
  • Crazy Happy Thing: Full length (01:37), 3 Short edits, 12 Loops
  • Have A Great Day: Full length (02:10), 4 Short edits, 13 Loops
  • Playground: Full length (01:22), No Fade In, 4 Short edits, 9 Loops
  • Teenage Love Story: Full length (02:14), No Fade In , 3 Short edits, 15 Loops
  • Carefree Romance: Full length (02:28), 2 Short edits, 10 Loops
  • Schoolgirl: Full length (02:21), 3 Short edits, 9 Loops
  • The Sweetest Victory: Full length (2:42), No Fade In, 2 Short edits, 12 Loops
  • Happy Adventures: Full length (01:41), 4 Short edits, 17 Loops


Take a look: Total Game Music Collection - 500 High Quality music themes ideal for any game!
